---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="HIP-1: Native Token Standard — Hyperliquid">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="text-zinc-500 text-sm hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">← Hyperliquid Overview</a>

    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4 mt-8">HIP-1</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Native Token Standard</span><span class="lang-zh">原生代幣標準</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">Every token on Hyperliquid gets a real order book — not an AMM pool. Launching one requires winning an auction, not clicking a button. This is anti-PumpFun by design.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">喺Hyperliquid上面每個token都自帶真正嘅order book — 唔係AMM pool。要launch一個token，你要贏一場auction，唔係㩒個掣咁簡單。成個設計就係同PumpFun對著幹。</span>
    </p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">How Token Deployment Works</span><span class="lang-zh">Token部署點樣運作</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Deploying a HIP-1 token is a multi-step process with real economic cost. The deployer specifies:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Deploy一個HIP-1 token唔係免費嘅，要經過幾個步驟，每步都要真金白銀。Deployer要設定以下參數：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Name</span> — up to 6 characters, no uniqueness requirement</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">名稱</span> — 最多6個字元，唔需要唯一</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">weiDecimals</span> — conversion rate from minimal units to human-readable format</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">weiDecimals</span> — 最小單位到人類可讀格式嘅轉換率</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">szDecimals</span> — minimum tradable decimals on spot order books (must satisfy <code>szDecimals + 5 ≤ weiDecimals</code>)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">szDecimals</span> — 現貨order book嘅最小可交易小數位（必須滿足 <code>szDecimals + 5 ≤ weiDecimals</code>）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">maxSupply</span> — initial and maximum supply (can only decrease through fees/burns)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">maxSupply</span> — 初始同最大供應量（只能通過fees/burns減少）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">initialWei</span> — optional genesis balances for treasuries or bridge mints</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">initialWei</span> — 可選嘅genesis餘額，用於treasury或bridge mint</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">anchorTokenWei</span> — existing HIP-1 tokens can receive proportional genesis allocations (airdrop mechanism)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">anchorTokenWei</span> — 現有HIP-1 token可以按比例獲得genesis分配（airdrop機制）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">hyperliquidityInit</span> — parameters for HIP-2 USDC spot pair initialization</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">hyperliquidityInit</span> — HIP-2 USDC現貨對嘅初始化參數</span></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Dutch Auction</span><span class="lang-zh">荷蘭式拍賣</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Token deployment operates through a <span class="text-white font-medium">31-hour Dutch auction</span>. The gas price decreases linearly from an initial price down to 500 HYPE (~$12,500). Rules:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Token部署通過一個<span class="text-white font-medium">31小時荷蘭式拍賣</span>進行。Gas價格從初始價格線性遞減到500 HYPE（~$12,500）。規則：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en">If the previous auction <span class="text-white">failed</span>: initial price = 500 HYPE</span><span class="lang-zh">如果上一次拍賣<span class="text-white">失敗</span>：初始價格 = 500 HYPE</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">If the previous auction <span class="text-white">succeeded</span>: initial price = 2x the last winning gas price</span><span class="lang-zh">如果上一次拍賣<span class="text-white">成功</span>：初始價格 = 上次中標gas價格嘅2倍</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">Gas <span class="text-white">cannot be refunded</span> if the deployment gets stuck — test on testnet first</span><span class="lang-zh">部署卡住嘅話，Gas<span class="text-white">退唔返</span> — 記得先喺testnet試</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">This auction mechanism is the core of HIP-1's design philosophy: <span class="text-white">high barrier to entry creates high signal</span>. Every token that makes it through the auction represents a meaningful economic commitment, unlike PumpFun where anyone can launch a token for ~$2.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">呢個拍賣機制就係HIP-1嘅核心理念：<span class="text-white">門檻高，質素先高</span>。過到拍賣嘅token，背後都係真金白銀嘅承諾，唔似PumpFun俾你用~$2就隨便開個幣。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Fee Structure & Distribution</span><span class="lang-zh">費用結構同分配</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Fee Type</span><span class="lang-zh">費用類型</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Destination</span><span class="lang-zh">去向</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Non-USDC fees (base token)</span><span class="lang-zh">Non-USDC費用（base token）</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">100% to deployer (default)</span><span class="lang-zh">100%歸deployer（默認）</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Unclaimed base token fees</span><span class="lang-zh">未領取嘅base token費用</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Burned</span><span class="lang-zh">銷毀</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Quote token (USDC) fees</span><span class="lang-zh">Quote token（USDC）費用</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Assistance Fund</span><span class="lang-zh">援助基金</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Deployers can adjust their fee share <span class="text-white">downward only</span> — once reduced, it can't be raised back. This prevents bait-and-switch dynamics.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Deployers只可以將fee share<span class="text-white">向下調</span> — 降咗就加唔返。防止先引你入局再加價。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Anchor Token Airdrops</span><span class="lang-zh">Anchor Token空投</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">A unique feature: new tokens can airdrop to holders of an existing HIP-1 token. Using <code>anchorTokenWei</code>, deployers specify proportional allocations. Holders must own at least 0.0001% of the anchor token's max supply to qualify. This creates a native on-chain airdrop mechanism without snapshot tooling or Merkle trees.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">一個獨特功能：新token可以空投畀現有HIP-1 token嘅持有者。使用<code>anchorTokenWei</code>，deployers指定按比例分配。持有者必須擁有至少anchor token最大供應量嘅0.0001%先有資格。呢個創建咗一個native鏈上空投機制，唔需要snapshot工具或Merkle trees。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Spot Dust Clearing</span><span class="lang-zh">現貨碎幣清理</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Daily at 00:00 UTC, balances under 1 lot size with notional value ≤ $1 are automatically aggregated and market-sold. Proceeds redistribute proportionally to affected users. Clearing pauses if the book is one-sided or dust impact exceeds thresholds ($10,000 for PURR, $3,000 for others). This keeps accounts clean without manual intervention.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">每日00:00 UTC，低於1 lot size且名義價值≤$1嘅餘額自動匯總並市價賣出。收益按比例重新分配畀受影響嘅用戶。如果order book只有單邊或dust影響超過閾值（PURR為$10,000，其他為$3,000），清理暫停。呢個保持賬戶清潔，唔需要手動介入。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">How the Spot Order Book Works</span><span class="lang-zh">現貨Order Book點樣運作</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Every HIP-1 token automatically gets a <span class="text-white font-medium">USDC spot order book</span> — no external DEX, no AMM pool, no liquidity bootstrapping needed. The order book is native to the L1.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">每個HIP-1 token都自動獲得一個<span class="text-white font-medium">USDC現貨order book</span> — 唔需要外部DEX，唔需要AMM pool，唔需要引導流動性。Order book係L1原生嘅。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Two decimal parameters control precision:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">兩個小數位參數控制精度：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">weiDecimals</span> — internal precision. This is how many decimal places the chain uses to store balances (like wei for ETH).</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">weiDecimals</span> — 內部精度。鏈用幾多個小數位嚟儲存餘額（好似ETH嘅wei咁）。</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">szDecimals</span> — minimum tradable unit on the order book. This is the smallest increment you can place an order for.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">szDecimals</span> — order book上嘅最小可交易單位。你可以落單嘅最細粒度。</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The constraint <code>szDecimals + 5 ≤ weiDecimals</code> ensures there's always enough internal precision to handle dust and rounding from order book operations. Without this gap, rounding errors would accumulate.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">約束條件 <code>szDecimals + 5 ≤ weiDecimals</code> 確保內部精度永遠足夠處理order book操作產生嘅碎幣同捨入。冇呢個差距嘅話，捨入誤差會越積越大。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Order mechanics:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">落單機制：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Order size in wei</span> = <code>sz × 10^(weiDecimalsBase − szDecimalsBase)</code></span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">以wei計嘅訂單大小</span> = <code>sz × 10^(weiDecimalsBase − szDecimalsBase)</code></span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Order value in quote wei</span> = <code>px × sz × 10^(weiDecimalsQuote − szDecimalsQuote)</code></span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">以quote wei計嘅訂單價值</span> = <code>px × sz × 10^(weiDecimalsQuote − szDecimalsQuote)</code></span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">Quote token is always <span class="text-white">Spot USDC</span> (szDecimals = weiDecimals = 8)</span><span class="lang-zh">Quote token永遠係<span class="text-white">Spot USDC</span>（szDecimals = weiDecimals = 8）</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Native spot and perps share <span class="text-white">identical volume-based fee schedules</span> — no separate fee tiers for spot vs derivatives. Your trading volume across both markets counts toward the same fee tier.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">原生現貨同永續合約共享<span class="text-white">同一套基於交易量嘅費率</span> — 唔會因為現貨定衍生品而收唔同費用。你喺兩個市場嘅交易量會計入同一個費率等級。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Anchor Token Airdrop — How It Works</span><span class="lang-zh">Anchor Token空投 — 詳細運作</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The <code>anchorTokenWei</code> parameter lets deployers distribute new tokens proportionally to holders of an existing HIP-1 token — no snapshot tooling, no Merkle trees, no claim contracts. It's all handled at the protocol level during token creation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><code>anchorTokenWei</code> 參數畀deployers可以按比例將新token分派畀現有HIP-1 token嘅持有者 — 唔使snapshot工具，唔使Merkle trees，唔使claim合約。全部喺token創建時由協議層處理。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Eligibility rules:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">資格規則：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en">Holders must hold at least <span class="text-white">0.0001%</span> of the anchor token's <code>maxSupply</code> to qualify</span><span class="lang-zh">持有者必須持有至少anchor token <code>maxSupply</code> 嘅<span class="text-white">0.0001%</span>先有資格</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">Distribution is proportional to <code>(balance − 1e-6 × anchorTokenMaxSupply)</code></span><span class="lang-zh">分配比例按照 <code>(balance − 1e-6 × anchorTokenMaxSupply)</code> 計算</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">The subtraction prevents dust holders from diluting real holders' allocations</span><span class="lang-zh">減去嗰部分防止碎幣持有者攤薄真正持有者嘅分配</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Concrete example:</span> Say PURR has a <code>maxSupply</code> of 1 billion. You hold 10 million PURR (1% of max supply). A new token launches with <code>anchorTokenWei</code> set to airdrop to PURR holders. You'd receive 1% of the new token's <code>anchorTokenWei</code> allocation — directly into your wallet at genesis, no claim needed.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">實例：</span>假設PURR嘅 <code>maxSupply</code> 係10億。你持有1,000萬個PURR（最大供應量嘅1%）。一個新token launch時設定咗 <code>anchorTokenWei</code> 空投畀PURR持有者。你會收到新token <code>anchorTokenWei</code> 分配嘅1% — 直接喺genesis時入你錢包，唔使claim。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">This creates a <span class="text-white">native airdrop pipeline</span> built into the token standard itself — a fundamentally different approach from EVM airdrops that require off-chain snapshots, Merkle proof generation, and separate claim contracts.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">呢個機制喺token標準入面建立咗一個<span class="text-white">原生空投管道</span> — 同EVM嗰套需要鏈下snapshot、生成Merkle proof、另外部署claim合約嘅做法完全唔同。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">From HIP-1 to HIP-2: The Full Launch Flow</span><span class="lang-zh">由HIP-1到HIP-2：完整Launch流程</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The end-to-end flow from auction to live trading:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">由拍賣到正式交易嘅完整流程：</span>
      </p>

      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Win the Dutch auction</span> — pay HYPE gas to secure a token deployment slot</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">贏得荷蘭式拍賣</span> — 支付HYPE gas嚟獲得token部署名額</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Token created</span> — on-chain with your specified parameters (name, supply, decimals, initial balances)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Token創建</span> — 喺鏈上按你設定嘅參數生成（名稱、供應量、小數位、初始餘額）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">USDC spot order book goes live</span> — native order book, ready for limit and market orders</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">USDC現貨order book上線</span> — 原生order book，可以落限價單同市價單</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">HIP-2 Hyperliquidity activates</span> — if <code>hyperliquidityInit</code> was set, automated market-making kicks in immediately</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">HIP-2 Hyperliquidity啟動</span> — 如果設定咗 <code>hyperliquidityInit</code>，自動做市即刻開始</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Deployer's seeded USDC provides initial depth</span> — buy-side liquidity from the deployer's commitment</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Deployer注入嘅USDC提供初始深度</span> — 買方流動性來自deployer嘅資金承諾</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Trading begins</span> — automated HIP-2 liquidity and organic orders coexist on the same order book</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">交易開始</span> — HIP-2自動流動性同有機訂單喺同一個order book上共存</span></li>
      </ol>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The whole process is <span class="text-white font-medium">permissionless and takes one transaction</span> after winning the auction. No governance vote, no whitelisting, no liquidity provider coordination.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">成個過程<span class="text-white font-medium">無需許可，贏完拍賣之後一個交易搞掂</span>。唔使governance投票，唔使白名單，唔使協調流動性提供者。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Real Examples: HYPE and PURR</span><span class="lang-zh">實際例子：HYPE同PURR</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">HYPE</span> is the native token of Hyperliquid — the first HIP-1 token. It serves as:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">HYPE</span> 係Hyperliquid嘅原生token — 第一個HIP-1 token。佢嘅用途包括：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en">Staking token for validator security</span><span class="lang-zh">驗證者安全嘅質押token</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">Gas token for Dutch auctions (deployer bonds)</span><span class="lang-zh">荷蘭式拍賣嘅gas token（deployer保證金）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en">The benchmark for auction pricing (initial price denominated in HYPE)</span><span class="lang-zh">拍賣定價嘅基準（初始價格以HYPE計價）</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">PURR</span> is a community memecoin — one of the first HIP-1 launches. It's become the de facto <span class="text-white">anchor token</span> for subsequent airdrops, meaning PURR holders regularly receive genesis allocations of new tokens. This makes PURR function like a "meta-token" — holding it gives you exposure to the entire HIP-1 ecosystem.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">PURR</span> 係一個社區memecoin — 最早期嘅HIP-1 launch之一。佢已經變成後續空投嘅事實<span class="text-white">anchor token</span>，意味住PURR持有者會定期收到新token嘅genesis分配。令PURR變成一個「meta-token」 — 持有佢就等於exposure成個HIP-1生態。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Both HYPE and PURR demonstrate the full HIP-1 + HIP-2 pipeline working in production — from auction to order book to automated liquidity to organic trading, all on a single L1.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">HYPE同PURR都證明咗完整嘅HIP-1 + HIP-2管道喺生產環境中運作 — 由拍賣到order book到自動流動性到有機交易，全部喺同一個L1上面。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">HIP-1 vs Other Token Standards</span><span class="lang-zh">HIP-1同其他代幣標準比較</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-white font-medium">HIP-1</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium">ERC-20</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium">SPL Token</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-500"><span class="lang-en">Launch cost</span><span class="lang-zh">發行成本</span></td>
